Add a *path operation* using an HTTP DELETE operation.

        ## Example

        ```python
        from fastapi import FastAPI

        app = FastAPI()

        @app.delete("/items/{item_id}")
        def delete_item(item_id: str):
            return {"message": "Item deleted"}
        ```
